name: 甘奈
text:
あっ……プロデューサさん
ごめん、なんか……緊張しちゃってて
trans:
Ah… Producer-san, sorry.
I think... I'm getting a bit nervous.

name: プロデューサー
text:
今日はリハーサルだ
もう少し、肩の力を抜いてもいいんだぞ
trans:
It's just a rehearsal for today so you can relax 
a little bit, it's alright.

name: 甘奈
text: えへへ……ちょっと気合入りすぎちゃった、かな……！
trans:
Ehehe... I might have pushed my myself a bit too much 
today...!

name: プロデューサー
text:
気合を入れるのは良いことだ
でも、千雪や甜花も一緒にいるんだから
trans:
Giving it your all is great, but it's alright since
Chiyuki and Tenka are here with you today.

name: 甘奈
text:
う、うん！　そうだよね
甘奈も……千雪さんや甜花ちゃんみたいに……
trans:
Y-Yeah! You're right. I can do it too...
Just like Chiyuki-san and Tenka-chan...
